# Docs + Module Map Sync

- When adding/moving modules or projects, update `docs/ai/repo-map.md` and `docs/ai/module-map.yml`.
- When adding DB objects or schemas, update `db/**/*` scripts and any relevant docs under `docs/architecture/` or `docs/adr/`.
- Keep ADR references and repo-map sections current; remove outdated “planned” entries once implemented.

## Examples

```text
// ✅ GOOD: new project added
Update docs/ai/repo-map.md and docs/ai/module-map.yml to include src/Api.SmokeTests/
```

```text
// ✅ GOOD: new schema objects added
Update db/** scripts and add/refresh docs/architecture notes about the schema
```
